          Questions about these terms? Reach us at <a href="mailto:info@growthwavecapital.com" class="font-semibold underline" style="color: #7C3AED;">info@growthwavecapital.com</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 p-5 rounded-lg border" style="background: #f9fafb; border-color: #e5e7eb;">
